    "description": "《Koumajou Remilia: Scarlet Symphony》是一款以“东方Project”角色为主角的横版动作游戏。自首次发布以来就受到了许多玩家的喜爱。因出色的游戏性，恢弘的配乐，再加上插画师晩杯あきら（Banpai Akira）对于东方角色的狂气、哥特式诠释而广受好评。<br><br>本作是原版游戏的增强版，支持HD重制图像和各种附加功能。为了让更多玩家享受灵梦的冒险之旅，游戏现已支持包括简体中文在内的6种语言。此外，作为增强版的独家要素，本作支持全配音，且由知名声优联袂出演。原版游戏和东方Project的粉丝务必不能错过。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>＜ 日语CV名单 ＞</strong></h2>• 博丽灵梦（CV：佐藤利奈）<br><br>• 雾雨魔理沙（CV：新谷凉子）<br>• 蕾米莉亚·斯卡蕾特（CV：喜多村英梨）<br>• 十六夜咲夜（CV：泽城美雪）<br>• 琪露诺（CV：悠木碧）<br>• 红美铃（CV：佐藤聪美）<br>• 帕秋莉·诺蕾姬（CV：力丸乃梨子）<br>• 爱丽丝·玛格特洛依德（CV：户松遥）<br>• 伊吹萃香（CV：冈咲美保）<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2>突然有一天，红雾卷土重来，再度将幻想乡笼罩其中。然而，博丽灵梦对这般异象再熟悉不过了。<br><br>“又是那吸血鬼做的好事？”她心里如此想着。<br><br>眼下唯一的选择，那便是：<br>赶往红魔馆，查明异变的真相。<br><br>……但这一次，通往宅邸的道路不同以往。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色</strong></h2><strong>由角色对话推进的故事</strong><br>玩家化身为博丽灵梦，探寻红雾的起因。在前往红魔馆的路途中，还会邂逅多名东方角色，进行多场激烈的弹幕战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/b9523c4e085aa4db6e60434fc56cb734.poster.avif?t=1659001031\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/b9523c4e085aa4db6e60434fc56cb734.webm?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/b9523c4e085aa4db6e60434fc56cb734.mp4?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>灵梦的武器——“大币”和“御札”</strong><br>灵梦不仅能够挥舞近战武器“大币”，还可以用“御札”发动远程攻击。根据战斗情况，合理利用武器。此外，她还有“飞行”的能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/c94015f0b02dfde68e19719798e02ef5.poster.avif?t=1659001031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/c94015f0b02dfde68e19719798e02ef5.webm?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/c94015f0b02dfde68e19719798e02ef5.mp4?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/54a2f0a075a74948c453b6361b3701d2.poster.avif?t=1659001031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/54a2f0a075a74948c453b6361b3701d2.webm?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/54a2f0a075a74948c453b6361b3701d2.mp4?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>魔理沙和琪露诺伴你左右！</strong><br>雾雨魔理沙和琪露诺将加入灵梦的冒险之旅，成为同伴并肩作战。玩家可以消耗御灵召唤它们。在合适的时机进行召唤，才能在战斗中占据上风。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/12787b02e90ba29421a7400b99a6fcab.poster.avif?t=1659001031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/12787b02e90ba29421a7400b99a6fcab.webm?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/12787b02e90ba29421a7400b99a6fcab.mp4?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/0d759eefe6fc04de10c7c2c51ecd00c3.poster.avif?t=1659001031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/0d759eefe6fc04de10c7c2c51ecd00c3.webm?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/0d759eefe6fc04de10c7c2c51ecd00c3.mp4?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>投身于激烈的弹幕战，与众多东方角色一决高下！</strong><br>玩家将扮演博丽灵梦，与红美玲、十六夜咲夜、爱丽丝·玛格特洛依德等东方角色一决高下。躲避花样百出的弹幕，把握时机反制对方。<br>而站在红魔馆众多强敌身后的，正是灵梦一路追踪的吸血鬼……！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/e4c0762d2a64ab031512ab53e68406fd.poster.avif?t=1659001031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/e4c0762d2a64ab031512ab53e68406fd.webm?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/e4c0762d2a64ab031512ab53e68406fd.mp4?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/55e6891b36ca9519dafd0b427176990c.poster.avif?t=1659001031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/55e6891b36ca9519dafd0b427176990c.webm?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/55e6891b36ca9519dafd0b427176990c.mp4?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/2969ae9ccac670007959e5031cbd82dd.poster.avif?t=1659001031\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/2969ae9ccac670007959e5031cbd82dd.webm?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229880/extras/2969ae9ccac670007959e5031cbd82dd.mp4?t=1659001031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>“伊吹萃香”作为新同伴加入！</strong><br>爱好酒席和美酒的“鬼”伊吹萃香在红魔城等待灵梦的到来。在本作中，她将与灵梦并肩作战，成为第三名同伴！消耗御灵，施展她的独特技能以击败敌人。<br><br><strong>极易模式！</strong><br>尽管本作难度较高，但内置极易模式，即便是不擅长动作射击游戏的玩家也能玩到最后。在游戏开局便可选择该模式。<br><br>与原版相比，《Koumajou Remilia: Scarlet Symphony》包含内置挑战、BGM合集、画廊等追加要素，绝对能满足新手和挑战爱好者的要求。",
